<a name="GoConqr">
<h4>
1.5.3. GoConqr
</h4>
	<p>
		GoConqr is the state of the art test generating software that allows multiple advanced features.<br>
		It's friendly UI allows students and teachers to feel welcomed as they enter the "testing room".</br>
		This software contains many features such as alerts as test reminders, allows a group to work on</br>
		the test together, and lastly, it allows the test to be grouped under subjects. <br><br>
	<p>
		Overall, this test generating website provides a truely state-of-the-art algorithm and functionality<br>
		that many others does not have
	<p>
		
	<b>Good Features:</b>
		<ul>
			<li> Allows to create an interactive "mind map" to see the conections of topics</li>
			<li> Able to create MC question quizzes</li>
			<li> Can create flash cards to share </li>
			<li> Allows fill in the blank questions</li>
			<li> UI is friendly</li>
			<li> It has a private message option for in page messages</li>
			<li> Display option for friends' activities (FB newfeed like feature)</li>
			<li> Allows students to take notes to build an online study hub</li>
	
		</ul>
		<p> 
		<strong>Bad Features:</strong>
		<ul>
			<li> Can not include pictures in questions</li>
			<li> Does not have a testbank</li>
			<li> Does not have an export option for results</li>
		</ul>
		<p>
		<strong>Missing Features:</strong>
		<ul>
			<li> an api</li>
			<li> database to store questions</li>
			<li> many features requires purchase </li>
		</ul>

